eviously accused of indecently assaulting 10 women and sexually assaulting another in alleged incidents dating back to 1976 when he was at the height of his fame.</p><p>The jury of eight women and four men deliberated for more than 20 hours before finding him not guilty of 12 indecent assault charges.</p><p>They were not, however, able to agree on a charge of alleged indecent assault against a woman in the early 1990s or an alleged sexual assault in 2008.</p>","headline":"Dave Lee Travis to face new charge of indecent assault","trailText":"The former Radio 1 DJ and BBC presenter was cleared of 12 counts of indecent assault last month","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/13/1392311392524/Dave-Lee-Travis-006.jpg","wordcount":"172","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-03-31T13:32:25Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk-news/2014/mar/28/dave-lee-travis-new-charge-indecent-assault","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/uk-news/2014/mar/28/dave-lee-travis-new-charge-indecent-assault","tags":[{"id":"uk/uk","webTitle":"UK news","type":"keyword","sectionId":"uk-news","sectionName":"UK news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/uk/uk","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/uk/uk","references":[]},{"id":"tone/news","webTitle":"News","type":"tone","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/tone/news","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/tone/news","references":[]},{"id":"type/article","webTitle":"Article","type":"type","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/articles","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/type/article","references":[]}],"references":[],"elements":[{"id":"gu-image-433221946","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/13/1392311398897/Dave-Lee-Travis-011.jpg","typeData":{"source":"Reuters","photographer":"Toby Melville","altText":"Dave Lee Travis","height":"276","c